videos.headline: Javaris comes up with 23-yard interception
videos.description: Auburn's Javaris Davis intercepts Tanner Morgan's pass and returns it 23 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Javaris comes up with 23-yard interception) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Igbinoghene returns kickoff for 96-yard TD
videos.description: Noah Igbinoghene fields a Minnesota kickoff and breaks free for a 96-yard Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Igbinoghene returns kickoff for 96-yard TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Ibrahim runs in a 16-yard TD
videos.description: Mohamed Ibrahim pushes through defenders and into the end zone for a 16-yard Minnesota touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Ibrahim runs in a 16-yard TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Johnson's somersault falls just short of TD
videos.description: Minnesota's Tyler Johnson leaps into the air for what is originally ruled a touchdown, but the call is overturned and he is marked short at the one-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Johnson's somersault falls just short of TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Green connects with Witham for Minnesota TD on 4th down
videos.description: Seth Green finds Bryce Witham for a one-yard Minnesota touchdown on 4th down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Green connects with Witham for Minnesota TD on 4th down) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Nix, Cannella link up for 37-yard TD
videos.description: Bo Nix runs around defenders and finds a wide-open Sal Cannella, who gets into the end zone for a 37-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Nix, Cannella link up for 37-yard TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Johnson makes wild, one-handed TD grab
videos.description: Minnesota's Tyler Johnson makes a leaping, one-handed touchdown catch, barely keeping his foot in bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Johnson makes wild, 1-handed TD grab) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Williams makes lunging catch on the sideline
videos.description: Bo Nix finds Seth Williams, who lunges for the off-balance catch for a 15-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Williams makes lunging catch on the sideline) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Morgan, Johnson link up for 73-yard TD
videos.description: Tanner Morgan goes deep to Tyler Johnson, who runs in for a 73-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Morgan, Johnson link up for 73-yard TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Fleck goes off on referee over clock adjustment
videos.description: P.J. Fleck gives a referee an earful after he notices there was an error with the time of the game clock in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fleck goes off on referee over clock adjustment) 2020/01/01 ESHEET
